claims:
1.一种分布式锂电池组储能系统，其特征在于：包括若干用于并联到直流母线上的储能控制单元；储能控制单元之间通过总线通信进行数据共享；1. A distributed lithium battery pack energy storage system, characterized in that: comprising several energy storage control units for being connected in parallel to the DC bus; data sharing is performed between the energy storage control units through bus communication;


         储能控制单元包括由单体锂电池组成的电池组、双向直流变换器、微控制器以及用于采集储能控制单元的状态监测数据的状态监测模块；电池组通过双向直流变换器从直流母线上获取电能或者输出电能到直流母线上；微控制器通过控制双向直流变换器来切换储能控制单元的充/放电模式；The energy storage control unit includes a battery pack composed of a single lithium battery, a bidirectional DC converter, a microcontroller, and a state monitoring module for collecting the status monitoring data of the energy storage control unit; the battery pack is connected from the DC bus through the bidirectional DC converter. It can obtain electric energy or output electric energy to the DC bus; the microcontroller switches the charging/discharging mode of the energy storage control unit by controlling the bidirectional DC converter;


         状态监测模块包括前端状态监测模块与后端状态监测模块；前端状态监测模块接入电池组与双向直流变换器之间，用于采集电池组的状态监测数据；后端状态监测模块接入双向直流变换器与直流母线之间，用于采集双向直流变换器的状态监测数据；The status monitoring module includes a front-end status monitoring module and a back-end status monitoring module; the front-end status monitoring module is connected between the battery pack and the bidirectional DC converter to collect status monitoring data of the battery pack; the back-end status monitoring module is connected to the bidirectional DC Between the converter and the DC bus, it is used to collect the state monitoring data of the bidirectional DC converter;


         每个微控制器内均配置有独立充电控制程序，所述独立充电控制程序用于根据对应储能控制单元的状态监测数据与直流母线电压UA确定相应储能控制单元的充电模式；Each microcontroller is equipped with an independent charging control program, and the independent charging control program is used to determine the charging mode of the corresponding energy storage control unit according to the state monitoring data of the corresponding energy storage control unit and the DC bus voltage U A ;


         独立充电控制程序包括如下步骤：The independent charging control procedure includes the following steps:


         步骤char1：获取直流母线电压UA，判断直流母线电压UA是否大于设定母线电压U1，所述设定母线电压U1大于额定直流母线电压；若否，则结束程序；若是，则启动独立充电控制程序，并进入步骤char2；Step char1: Obtain the DC bus voltage U A , determine whether the DC bus voltage U A is greater than the set bus voltage U 1 , and the set bus voltage U1 is greater than the rated DC bus voltage; if not, end the program; if so, start the independent Charge control program, and enter step char2;


         步骤char2：根据状态监测数据判断储能控制单元是否为故障状态，若是，则储能控制单元退出运行，并结束程序；若否，则进入步骤char3；Step char2: According to the state monitoring data, determine whether the energy storage control unit is in a fault state, if so, the energy storage control unit exits the operation and ends the program; if not, then goes to step char3;


         步骤char3：判断电池组端电压UB是否小于设定端电压U2，所述设定端电压U2为单体电池的最大工作电压；若是，进入步骤char4；若否，进入步骤char5；Step char3: determine whether the battery pack terminal voltage U B is less than the set terminal voltage U 2 , the set terminal voltage U2 is the maximum working voltage of the single battery; if so, go to step char4; if not, go to step char5;


         步骤char4：微控制器控制双向直流变换器切换至恒流充电模式对电池组进行充电，并回到步骤char3；Step char4: The microcontroller controls the bidirectional DC converter to switch to the constant current charging mode to charge the battery pack, and returns to step char3;


         步骤char5：微控制器控制双向直流变换器切换至恒压充电模式对电池组进行充电，直到充电完成；Step char5: The microcontroller controls the bidirectional DC converter to switch to the constant voltage charging mode to charge the battery pack until the charging is completed;


         每个微控制器内均配置有协同放电控制程序，所述协同放电控制程序用于根据共享数据与直流母线电压UA确定整体放电模式；共享数据包括负载功率、每个电池组的剩余电量以及每个电池组的额定输出功率。A cooperative discharge control program is configured in each microcontroller, and the cooperative discharge control program is used to determine the overall discharge mode according to the shared data and the DC bus voltage U A ; the shared data includes the load power, the remaining power of each battery pack, and Rated output power of each battery pack.

3.根据权利要求1所述的分布式锂电池组储能系统，其特征在于：双向直流变换器的状态监测数据包括双向直流变换器的输出电压、双向直流变换器的输出电流；3. The distributed lithium battery pack energy storage system according to claim 1, wherein the state monitoring data of the bidirectional DC converter comprises the output voltage of the bidirectional DC converter and the output current of the bidirectional DC converter;


         以双向直流变换器的输出电压作为直流母线电压UA；微控制器根据直流母线电压UA作为启动充电或是放电的判据：当直流母线电压UA大于设定母线电压U1时，启动独立充电控制程序；当直流母线电压UA小于等于设定母线电压U1时，启动协同放电控制程序；Take the output voltage of the bidirectional DC converter as the DC bus voltage U A ; the microcontroller uses the DC bus voltage U A as the criterion for starting charging or discharging: when the DC bus voltage U A is greater than the set bus voltage U 1 , start Independent charging control program; when the DC bus voltage U A is less than or equal to the set bus voltage U 1 , the coordinated discharge control program is started;


         双向直流变换器的输出电压与双向直流变换器的输出电流作为微控制器控制双向直流变换器实现不同放电模式的依据。The output voltage of the bidirectional DC converter and the output current of the bidirectional DC converter are used as the basis for the microcontroller to control the bidirectional DC converter to realize different discharge modes.

5.根据权利要求1所述的分布式锂电池组储能系统，其特征在于：协同放电控制程序包括以下步骤：5. The distributed lithium battery pack energy storage system according to claim 1, wherein the coordinated discharge control program comprises the following steps:


         步骤dis1：获取直流母线电压UA，判断直流母线电压UA是否小于等于设定母线电压U1，若否，则结束程序；若是，则启动协同放电控制程序，并进入步骤dis2；Step dis1: obtain the DC bus voltage UA , determine whether the DC bus voltage UA is less than or equal to the set bus voltage U 1 , if not, end the program; if so, start the coordinated discharge control program, and enter step dis2;


         步骤dis2：根据状态监测数据判断储能控制单元是否能够工作，若否，则储能控制单元退出运行，并结束程序；若是，则进入步骤dis3；Step dis2: judge whether the energy storage control unit can work according to the state monitoring data, if not, the energy storage control unit exits the operation, and ends the program; if so, enter step dis3;


         步骤dis3：对电池组的剩余电量SOC进行数据共享；计算全部能够工作的储能控制单元的额定输出功率总和，并与负载功率进行比较：若额定输出功率总和能够满足负载功率，则进入步骤dis4；若额定输出功率总和不能够满足负载功率，则进入步骤dis5；Step dis3: share data on the remaining power SOC of the battery pack; calculate the sum of the rated output power of all the energy storage control units that can work, and compare it with the load power: if the sum of the rated output power can meet the load power, then go to step dis4 ; If the sum of the rated output power cannot meet the load power, then go to step dis5;


         步骤dis4：微控制器控制双向直流变换器切换至直流母线恒压放电模式；Step dis4: the microcontroller controls the bidirectional DC converter to switch to the DC bus constant voltage discharge mode;


         步骤dis5：微控制器控制双向直流变换器切换至恒功率放电模式：全部能够工作的储能控制单元均以额定功率进行输出；Step dis5: The microcontroller controls the bidirectional DC converter to switch to the constant power discharge mode: all the energy storage control units that can work are output at rated power;


         步骤dis6：判断直流母线电压UA是否能够维持在设定母线电压U1；若是，则回到步骤dis5；若否，则进入步骤dis7；Step dis6: determine whether the DC bus voltage U A can be maintained at the set bus voltage U 1 ; if so, go back to step dis5; if not, enter step dis7;


         步骤dis7：判断直流母线电压UA的下降程度是否达到第一下降度阈值；若否，则进入步骤dis8；若是，则进入步骤dis9；Step dis7: judging whether the degree of decline of the DC bus voltage UA reaches the first threshold of decline; if not, proceed to step dis8; if so, proceed to step dis9;


         步骤dis8：微控制器控制双向直流变换器维持恒功率放电模式，并回到步骤dis7；Step dis8: the microcontroller controls the bidirectional DC converter to maintain the constant power discharge mode, and returns to step dis7;


         步骤dis9：微控制器控制双向直流变换器切换至恒流放电模式：全部能够工作的储能控制单元均以恒定电流输出；Step dis9: The microcontroller controls the bidirectional DC converter to switch to the constant current discharge mode: all the energy storage control units that can work are output at constant current;


         步骤dis10：判断直流母线电压UA的下降程度是否达到第二下降度阈值；若否，则进入步骤dis11；若是，则进入步骤dis12；Step dis10: judging whether the degree of decline of the DC bus voltage UA reaches the second threshold of decline; if not, proceed to step dis11; if so, proceed to step dis12;


         步骤dis11：微控制器控制双向直流变换器维持恒流放电模式，并回到步骤dis10；Step dis11: The microcontroller controls the bidirectional DC converter to maintain the constant current discharge mode, and returns to step dis10;


         步骤dis12：微控制器向上位机发送切负荷请求或者控制储能控制单元退出运行。Step dis12: The microcontroller sends a load shedding request to the upper computer or controls the energy storage control unit to exit operation.

6.根据权利要求5所述的分布式锂电池组储能系统，其特征在于：直流母线恒压放电模式包括如下步骤：6. The distributed lithium battery pack energy storage system according to claim 5, wherein the DC bus constant voltage discharge mode comprises the following steps:


         步骤401：根据负载功率确定所需投入的能够工作的储能控制单元的数量，选出相应数量的能够工作的储能控制单元作为工作模块；Step 401: Determine the number of working energy storage control units to be put in according to the load power, and select a corresponding number of working energy storage control units as working modules;


         步骤402：除剩余电量SOC最小的工作模块以外，其余工作模块输出额定功率Pn，剩余电量SOC最小的工作模块输出补充功率Pm，补充功率Pm＝(Pload-Psum)/N，N表示剩余电量SOC最小的工作模块数量，Pload表示负载功率，Psum表示其余工作模块输出功率总和。Step 402 : Except for the working module with the smallest remaining power SOC, the other working modules output the rated power P n , and the working module with the smallest remaining power SOC outputs the supplementary power P m , where the supplementary power P m =(P load -P sum )/N, N represents the number of working modules with the smallest remaining power SOC, P load represents the load power, and P sum represents the total output power of the remaining working modules.
